text: The reservation process was flawless. Since this was my first experience with renting an Air B&B, I wasn't familiar with the website so I didn't see the owners "House Manuel". I sent him a message and the response was quick and helpful as I was directed where to find it. The Manuel had all the information we needed to gain access to the home and all the small details, even how to work the telivision.
title: Walk/Bike to ACL, 6th St, UT Campus
